---
// Features.astro
---
<section id="como-funciona" class="py-24 bg-brand-lighter relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:24px_24px]"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-dark mb-4">A tecnologia por trás do seu lucro</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-text/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Não deixe bots e concorrentes torrarem seu orçamento. Veja como a Ratoeira Ads protege cada centavo investido.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="bg-brand-card/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/5 hover:border-brand-yellow/30 transition-colors hover:shadow-xl">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-yellow/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-yellow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-3">Bloqueio Inteligente</h4>
        <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Identificamos padrões suspeitos de cliques falsos, IPs concorrentes e fazendas de bots, bloqueando o acesso diretamente na fonte antes de gastar sua verba.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="bg-brand-card/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/5 hover:border-brand-yellow/30 transition-colors hover:shadow-xl">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-yellow/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-yellow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-3">Visibilidade Real (Tracking)</h4>
        <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Tenha 100% de clareza de onde vêm as suas vendas. Rastreamento nativo e marcadores independentes para você escalar sem depender das limitações das pixels.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="bg-brand-card/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/5 hover:border-brand-yellow/30 transition-colors hover:shadow-xl">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-yellow/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-yellow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-3">ROI Exponencial</h4>
        <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Otimize campanhas no nível do clique bruto. Ao parar de jogar dinheiro fora com fraudes, seu ROI e LU realizável sobem de forma exponencialmente mais rápida.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- UI Mockup Area -->
    <div class="mt-20 flex justify-center perspective-1000 relative">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-yellow/5 rounded-[40px] blur-[80px] z-0"></div>
      <img src="/mockup.png" alt="Ratoeira Ads Dashboard" class="w-full max-w-4xl h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] border border-black/10 z-10 transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
